data.description: Welcome to this fantastic investment opportunity! This 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom, 2-car garage home is a diamond in the rough, perfect for savvy investors and those with a keen eye for potential. Built-in 2021, this property offers a solid foundation with 1,820 sq ft of living space and a modern open-concept floor plan, providing a canvas for your creative vision.  Step into the living room, a blank slate ready for your personal touch and transformative ideas. This is the perfect space to unleash your creativity and add value to the property. The master bedroom is a true retreat, complete with a luxurious on-suite bathroom featuring a temperature control keypad and a refreshing rain shower for a spa-like experience.  The additional three bedrooms are versatile and can be customized to meet your specific needs – whether it's a guest room, a home office, or a hobby space.  Step outside to the screened-in lanai, a haven to enjoy the Florida sunshine while being protected from pests. The fenced backyard offers privacy and security, making it an ideal space for pets or outdoor activities.  Here's the exciting part – the seller is offering a generous flooring credit! Seize this opportunity to turn this property into the home of your dreams. Use the credit to create a living space that reflects your style and preferences. Don't miss out on this chance to invest in a property with incredible potential. Schedule a showing today and envision the possibilities that await you in this fixer-upper gem!
